            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, welcome Sophie. You've got a nice smile today, as usual."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Ehehe, really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. But..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "W-what is it...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Well, you're always wearing similar looking clothes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "You've got such a cute face, you should wear something more stylish."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Y-you think so...? But you're always wearing the same thing too, Tess."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I'm wearing this shop's uniform."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, right... By the way, are the bunny ears part of the uniform?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "No, this is my own original addition. The Meister allowed it, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Huh... Is Mr. Horst really into bunny ears or something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That's quite a misunderstanding. The rabbit ears are popular with the children, that's why I allowed them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "First time hearing that... I thought it was because it's popular with the male customers..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x20,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Ahem!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "W-we probably shouldn't push this issue too much further..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Y-yeah..."
        }
    ]
